  {
    "url": "https://www.tiktok.com/@thekatieromero/video/7623977231873821966",
    "post_id": "7623977231873821966",
    "description": "Here’s everything I did on day 2 of my solo trip to Lisbon, Portugal.  1. Breakfast at @dearbreakfast 2. Saturday morning flea market 📍 Feira da Ladra  3. Shopping at @refuse_shop, @brus_pt, @kintustudio_store, @thirdthriftstore, @lxfactory 4. Pizza at @lupita  #solotravel #lisbon #solotraveler #solofemaletravel #TravelReels\nDay 2 of my solo Lisbon trip! Enjoy breakfast at Dear Breakfast, explore the Feira da Ladra flea market, shop at LX Factory and more. #solotravel #lisbon #TravelReels\nMy solo adventure in Lisbon, Portugal continued on day two with a full itinerary packed with local experiences. The day began with a delightful breakfast at @dearbreakfast, setting a pleasant tone for the morning.\n\nFollowing breakfast, I immersed myself in the vibrant atmosphere of the Saturday morning flea market, Feira da Ladra. This traditional market is a treasure trove of antiques, crafts, and unique finds, offering a glimpse into local life.\n\nMy exploration then moved to shopping at some of Lisbon's well-known boutiques and thrift stores. I visited @refuse_shop, @brus_pt, @kintustudio_store, @thirdthriftstore, and the eclectic @lxfactory. LX Factory, in particular, is a hub of creativity, featuring independent shops, restaurants, and art installations.\n\nTo round off the day, I enjoyed a satisfying pizza dinner at @lupita.\n\n#solotravel #lisbon #solotraveler #solofemaletravel #TravelReels",
